## Usage Instructions

This file contains Gujarati translations for:
1. Disease names for CNN model predictions
2. Treatment recommendations for RAG responses
3. Chemical names for agricultural advice

The mappings are used by:
- CNN model for disease classification output
- RAG system for generating Gujarati responses
- Mobile app for displaying localized content
